headline: Is There an Opportunity in Lennar After Recent 4% Price Surge?
summary: Are you weighing whether to buy, hold, or let go of Lennar stock? You are not alone. With the price closing recently at $127.14, Lennar has posted a solid 3.8% return over the last seven days and is up 4.3% over the past thirty. Yet, if you zoom out, the year-to-date performance is still down at -5.4%, and the one-year return comes in at -18.9%. Looking back five years, the stock has climbed a remarkable 104.4%, which speaks to its long-term resilience. What is behind these recent moves? Much...
